{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/plot.png?t=1734044056\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turning away from\u00a0the stress of the\u00a0big city, you set sail for Horizon Island, a place far from civilisation, where a small community of\u00a0residents live a simple life in tune with nature. As their new chef, you will ensure that everyone gets fed. It's not so bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Not when\u00a0there's enough food to go around, at least.\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/the_gang.png?t=1734044056\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/features.png?t=1734044056\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unravel the mystery of Horizon Island, and discover the secrets lurking beneath this happy village of friendly animals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a variety of cooking minigames, and learn to make do when ingredients run low.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose which residents to spend time and build friendships which might just blossom into something more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a whole other side of your new best friends with 4 character-specific routes, each with multiple bloody conclusions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play over 4 seasons, each one a little less plentiful than the last.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replay to discover secret achievements which reward you for indulging your curiosity and making unconventional choices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/the_gang2.png?t=1